Prof Ndulu’s death came just two days after Tanzania lost its former Finance and Planning permanent secretary, Dr Servacius Likwelile. 

The two had some issues in common. Apart from their economics background, while Dr Likwelile once served as Treasury PS, Prof Ndulu served as BoT Governor for 10 years from 2008. 

At the time of his death, Dr Likwelile was an economics don at the University of Dar es Salaam (UDSM). 



